{"tid":810901,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］諗住整個platform撈open dataset做咩topic好","createTime":"2018-09-08T10:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T00:22:24.000Z","uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2df78664e917e24322a226bbeb0045a356e54f1","tid":810901,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"呢個係fyp黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要係去搵啲現有網上嘅open data<br />\n攞左落黎可以做啲data visualisation<br />\n整完比人打下飛機或者做其他野<br />\n但最緊要整到啲前人未整過嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我希望成品整完真係有人會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但諗唔到做咩topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n形式唔係重點（apps定乜7遲啲先決定）<br />\n<br />\n各位財經台巴打想要啲咩都可以提議下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟cs 同finance好多野都唔識<br />\n唔好預我整到好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be406a60970c547db9a78c039e0577664868bea","tid":810901,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"你讀咩架"},{"pid":"c25c18e178495eba0c279c26e667915dfecc5b8b","tid":810901,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"Noted <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529bed6b5bed6bd55ba130dde613009a5f790530","tid":810901,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be406a60970c547db9a78c039e0577664868bea","tid":810901,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"你讀咩架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"Computer science <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00aa88479bd9750f38dd09b2e73228cfa674d7e","tid":810901,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi